text:
@GOP South Korea and the US reported their first #COVID19 case the same day.

See when each ramped up their testing.

6 weeks later, SK had done 140,000 tests. US 1,500.

Deaths to date
SK 250 
US 66,760

One acted quickly, decisively.
Guess which.

#LostTime #LostLives
